}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "ESR-9752-1.00 LFP 7016A0251000" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The FCC test report lists the Sitecom WL-340, corega CG-WLBAR10, and [[Rosewill RNX-EasyN400]] as identical models.
